<div id="review_2626182764" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2626182764" />
    <a title="Mikhail" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/25772487-mikhail"><img alt="Mikhail" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1455476005p2/25772487.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2626182764?book_show_action=true">Dec 14, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mikhail" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mikhail" href="/user/show/25772487-mikhail">Mikhail</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/39333207-monk-s-hood">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2626182764" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10282057957945854304">Embarking on a not-terribly-in-order re-read of the Cadfael books, since I last read them when I was still in high school. The first few were a bit over-leisurely if still pleasant, but this one ramps it up. A much more active mystery (in the sense that Cadfael is up and about, and the narration focused fairly tightly on him), and a sidesplittingly hilarious post-mystery conclusion. Monk politics had me giggling at length.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

