        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3572486427" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16850664302093778806">Monk&apos;s Hood has always ranked among my favourite Cadfael stories, and unlike some of the other novels, I found I actually liked it as much as the TV adaptation (which did not change too much). Plus, the audiobook narrator does an excellent Welsh accent. <br/><br/>Well worth a read. I just wish Head of Zeus would put more of the Kindle editions on sale. </span>
  <span id="freeText16850664302093778806" style="display:none">Monk's Hood has always ranked among my favourite Cadfael stories, and unlike some of the other novels, I found I actually liked it as much as the TV adaptation (which did not change too much). Plus, the audiobook narrator does an excellent Welsh accent. <br /><br />Well worth a read. I just wish Head of Zeus would put more of the Kindle editions on sale. </span>
